WEBVTT

00:03:59.951 --> 00:04:02.767
brave Indian soldiers,

00:04:02.791 --> 00:04:07.207
and even refugees struggling 
the world’s largest crisis in Syria,

00:04:07.231 --> 00:04:09.527
with whom we spent 90
days in Europe last year --

00:04:10.101 --> 00:04:16.031
from each class of the society, 
even the common person's lives

00:04:16.031 --> 00:04:19.031
and life lessons might be celebrated.

00:04:19.031 --> 00:04:23.887
We try to understand
what other people are doing.

00:04:23.911 --> 00:04:28.407
This year, in Uttarakhand’s Tehri
district, with the help of Round Glass,

00:04:28.431 --> 00:04:30.887
we adopted a village.